{"tid":1365680,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"在外地既巴絲 要做靚香港人呢個品牌","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:51:48.000Z","uid":42691,"like":89,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"60c9bfea13f51b956e2d67517adb9229df4b090c","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完留學生毆鬥條片<br />\n發現好多鬼佬撐我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家全世界都知道hk is not china<br />\n我地要進一步區別兩種人種<br />\n外貌膚色冇得搞<br />\n但行為可以改變<br />\n目標係要變成<br />\n好似日本人同大陸人之間既分別咁<br />\n而我地要做上等人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n參考日本人既行為<br />\n1.人多密集情況下好少大聲講野<br />\n2.禮貌<br />\n3.有笑容<br />\n4.熱心幫人<br />\n5.世界盃會自備統一顏色既膠袋去執垃圾 弘揚國威<br />\n6.準時<br />\n7.sorry呢隻字唔洗錢 可以講多d<br />\n8.同樣地 講多d 廣東話既唔該 多謝"},{"pid":"e5533afee01a44589d56eb6022fbdf7e70ea4882","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:25:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"911a4a1a126eb617a553806d547aa8a5cc6c9228","tid":1365680,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"上邊果段冇咩野<br />\n睇到下邊1~8點<br />\n屌你膠post黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d4cbdfc82504af03293971f0f0eedaae21ab49","tid":1365680,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:24:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5fcc2ad0d9c37aaf0273e82ca06d8af6ad2f77ec","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911a4a1a126eb617a553806d547aa8a5cc6c9228","tid":1365680,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"上邊果段冇咩野<br />\n睇到下邊1~8點<br />\n屌你膠post黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"咁唔係應該點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349a487a22172cfe3c59d7e00c610770310d5ba9","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:56:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c380a6c7bce8dadf6354bcb326f20c1138ee98fe","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39d7acb014499298564a29870bc5ab716327b008","tid":1365680,"uid":271766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:13:44.000Z","msg":"Hong Kong is not fucking CHINA!<br />\nDIU NEI LO MO!"},{"pid":"6947625b39e41e15d108c0ef500734d8fc1d2952","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:33:53.000Z","msg":"[升級注意]連儂牆2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365831</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc7b8a4212bee09836de4ad4cbed95bb90e91147","tid":1365680,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:48:27.000Z","msg":"support, 香港人要再進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#搭lift可唔可以唔好講嘢，真係好撚應聲，勁吵耳，忍1,2 分鐘好無？"},{"pid":"a0f0571026dd5eaaf33439c38f555d695e6c2432","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"9.酒店退房可以簡單整理下<br />\n<br />\n發現好多香港人去完旅行 <br />\n臨走一定要整到亂曬先安樂<br />\n好似咁樣先賺到人地既服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果個個都以為香港人都係咁撚亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a08d5e24bc0554bc7a73e771023bd1091644ac","tid":1365680,"uid":137753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:16:45.000Z","msg":"推到香港成為東亞第一民族為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7246c883c7dbee9716217826139404e217f33775","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:18:36.000Z","msg":"10.外地食完快餐可以執下盤<br />\n<br />\n外地普遍都係自己執盤<br />\n做返大學時候既你就ok<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得好做作 好尷尬<br />\n請你抹乾淨張檯 執成一盤野 <br />\n等人地一拎就搞掂<br />\n原則就係唔為其他人帶來麻煩<br />\n<br />\n本地最好做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62fbb0fd0466e4faeb38f4a773538c7dc11d91ad","tid":1365680,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"Nice advice <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過 雖然Sorry 係唔洗錢，但唔洗講得多，成日sorry 會影響自信心，同埋可能會搞到俾人以為香港人好恰"},{"pid":"caed6da586f297e25fa2fff2c1210b695f3008a6","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:28:36.000Z","msg":"11.在外地好感激對方既時候<br />\n可以寫thank you letter<br />\n<br />\n就好似你好感激太古商場保安<br />\n無比既恩情唔知點報好<br />\n你可以寫信 幾句英文 一句港文<br />\n最後署名來自香港"},{"pid":"9d4c2cbd3e98a60e5781171e8ba27d22e734fcab","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"12.如果當日感覺自己正能量爆燈<br />\n請你多d同人交流 接觸<br />\n<br />\n一個人正能量爆燈既時候<br />\n多d同人點頭、投以微笑、握手、搭訕<br />\n少少既動作都會為人帶來溫暖"},{"pid":"108cfc3baa9f561c0149114031d779bd61841163","tid":1365680,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f0571026dd5eaaf33439c38f555d695e6c2432","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:13:27.000Z","msg":"9.酒店退房可以簡單整理下<br />\n<br />\n發現好多香港人去完旅行 <br />\n臨走一定要整到亂曬先安樂<br />\n好似咁樣先賺到人地既服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果個個都以為香港人都係咁撚亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:34:45.000Z","msg":"開頭我都同OP 有一樣嘅想法，直到睇到下面條link <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考下下面條link, 有日本如埋香港酒店業對於住客退房前執定房嘅感想<br />\n<br />\n酒店禮儀｜小心愈幫愈忙 房務員希望客人退房「維持原狀」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gotrip.hk/372267/travel_hacker/%e9%85%92%e5%ba%97%e7%a6%ae%e5%84%80-%e5%94%94%e5%a5%bd%e5%9f%b7%e6%88%bf-%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e4%bd%8f%e5%ae%bf/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2F372267%2Ftravel_hacker%2F%25e9%2585%2592%25e5%25ba%2597%25e7%25a6%25ae%25e5%2584%2580-%25e5%2594%2594%25e5%25a5%25bd%25e5%259f%25b7%25e6%2588%25bf-%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%259c%25ac%25e4%25bd%258f%25e5%25ae%25bf%2F&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hAy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=3c17d71c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gotrip.hk/372267/travel_hacker/%e9%85%92%e5%ba%97%e7%a6%ae%e5%84%80-%e5%94%94%e5%a5%bd%e5%9f%b7%e6%88%bf-%e6%97%a5%e6%9c%ac%e4%bd%8f%e5%ae%bf/</a>"},{"pid":"0efe768dc04c96a628ffc2b4bcf108b41809c6c8","tid":1365680,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d4c2cbd3e98a60e5781171e8ba27d22e734fcab","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:32:54.000Z","msg":"12.如果當日感覺自己正能量爆燈<br />\n請你多d同人交流 接觸<br />\n<br />\n一個人正能量爆燈既時候<br />\n多d同人點頭、投以微笑、握手、搭訕<br />\n少少既動作都會為人帶來溫暖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:36:04.000Z","msg":"This one really good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037b6b7df39f3ef229ad98ec56fd6864a13b5cc5","tid":1365680,"uid":42691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"13.帶走自己既煙頭<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以好型咁掉落地<br />\n但如果有一堆中國人係附近 <br />\n佢地都係掉落地既時候 <br />\n你應該<del>質落佢地把口度</del>自己帶走<br />\n<br />\n話比外國朋友聽 香港人錫自己地方<br />\n就好似日本人錫自己地方一樣<br />\n<br />\n陳雲話<br />\n世上只有我們是香港人<br />\n<br />